  tags: ['Melbourne', 'Cafes', 'Suburb analysis'],
  intro: 'Melbourne has more cafés per capita than almost any city in the world. That makes choosing the right suburb critical — the difference between a location with genuine commercial potential and one that is already oversaturated is not always obvious from the street. This analysis looks at 15 Melbourne suburbs through the lens of foot traffic, competition, demographics and rent.',
